LEAVE YOUR NATIVE LAND?

24:30.164 --> 24:32.732
-THE PEOPLE IN MY COUNTRY
ARE VERY BACKWARDS.

24:32.862 --> 24:35.909
THEY ONLY THINK OF MONEY.
THEY DON'T THINK ABOUT THE SOUL.

24:36.039 --> 24:38.520
YOU KNOW, MY FATHER IS ONE
OF THE RICHEST MEN
ON THE CONTINENT.

24:38.651 --> 24:41.523
OH, YES. AND ONE DAY,
I WILL INHERIT HIS FORTUNE.

24:41.654 --> 24:45.571
BUT UNTIL THEN, I AM
WHAT YOU MIGHT CONSIDER
AN INDEPENDENT BUSINESSMAN.

24:51.054 --> 24:53.361
-DO YOU MIND IF I TAKE OVER?
-YEAH.

24:55.581 --> 24:57.104
-COME ON, BUDDY,
SHARE THE WEALTH.

24:57.234 --> 24:58.758
-GET LOST.

25:07.897 --> 25:08.768
OKAY.

25:11.727 --> 25:13.816
-THANK YOU.
-ANY TIME.

25:37.666 --> 25:41.061
-YOU LOOK ABSOLUTELY
MAGNIFICENT.

25:42.062 --> 25:43.019
-THANK YOU.

25:43.716 --> 25:44.891
AND YOU LOOK GREAT.

25:46.849 --> 25:51.027
-WANT TO DANCE?
-YES.

26:10.612 --> 26:13.397
-WANT TO GO FOR A WALK?
-SURE.

26:18.228 --> 26:19.578
-YOU FEEL GOOD.

26:22.319 --> 26:23.190
-SO DO YOU.

26:53.220 --> 26:54.613
-CHECK IT OUT.

26:55.222 --> 26:58.094
-OH, I KNEW IT.
I KNEW THEY'D GET BACK TOGETHER.

26:58.225 --> 26:59.487
-HOW DID YOU KNOW?

27:00.793 --> 27:03.056
-OLD FLAMES ALWAYS CATCH FIRE
AGAIN ON A CRUISE.

27:04.753 --> 27:06.929
-YOU'VE BEEN WATCHING
TOO MANY "LOVE BOATS."

27:18.071 --> 27:18.941
-MITCH.

27:20.073 --> 27:22.336
-WHAT'S WRONG?
-WE CAN'T DO THIS.

27:22.466 --> 27:24.991
WE'VE BEEN DOWN
THIS ROAD BEFORE.
IT'S A DEAD END.

27:25.121 --> 27:27.297
-IT WAS A DEAD END,
BECAUSE YOU WERE MARRIED.

27:27.428 --> 27:30.039
YOU'RE NOT MARRIED NOW.
-NO, I'M SORRY.

27:31.693 --> 27:32.825
I DON'T KNOW WHAT IT WAS--

27:32.955 --> 27:35.131
THE MUSIC, THE CHAMPAGNE,

27:35.784 --> 27:37.090
THE WAY YOU LOOKED
IN THE MOONLIGHT--

27:37.743 --> 27:39.875
BUT I GOT CARRIED AWAY.
WE BOTH DID.

27:41.616 --> 27:43.009
-WHAT ARE YOU AFRAID OF?

27:45.359 --> 27:46.621
-CHANGE.

27:47.709 --> 27:49.319
I LIKE OUR RELATIONSHIP
THE WAY IT IS.

27:49.450 --> 27:51.887
I LIKE WORKING WITH YOU.
I LIKE SWIMMING WITH YOU.

27:52.018 --> 27:54.020
I LIKE BEING ABLE
TO TALK WITH YOU

27:54.150 --> 27:56.283
WITHOUT HAVING TO
WORRY ABOUT WHAT COMES NEXT.

27:57.284 --> 27:58.807
I LIKE BEING YOUR FRIEND.

27:58.938 --> 28:01.157
-STEPHANIE, I DON'T THINK
YOU KNOW WHAT YOU LIKE.

28:01.288 --> 28:03.246
YOU CHANGE YOUR MIND
EVERY TEN MINUTES.

28:04.726 --> 28:06.467
-I WAS JUST TRYING
TO BE SENSIBLE.

28:06.597 --> 28:07.686
-STEPHANIE.

28:14.954 --> 28:15.781
FINE.

28:17.739 --> 28:21.003
YOU WANT TO BE FRIENDS?
WE'LL BE FRIENDS.

28:21.917 --> 28:24.790
NO MORE GETTING CARRIED AWAY.
NO MORE CHAMPAGNE.

28:24.920 --> 28:29.098
NO MORE MUSIC. FROM NOW ON,
WE'RE JUST FRIENDS.
I GOT IT.

28:29.229 --> 28:32.841
-MITCH.
-NO, I GOT NO PROBLEM WITH THIS,
I REALLY DON'T.

28:32.972 --> 28:35.061
FRIENDS. NO PROBLEM. I GOT IT.

28:35.191 --> 28:36.627
WE ARE FRIENDS.

28:45.201 --> 28:46.768
-OH, GOD, WHAT HAVE I DONE?

28:48.901 --> 28:50.554
-TAKE ME NOW.

28:50.685 --> 28:52.382
-TAKE YOU WHERE? OOH!

28:52.513 --> 28:54.471
OH, MRS. KENILWORTH, PLE--
OH, PLEASE, PLEASE, PLEASE.

28:54.602 --> 28:56.560
MRS. KENILWORTH, DON'T DO THAT.
PLEASE, COME ON.

28:56.691 --> 28:58.171
OH, PLEASE, PLEASE.
OH, IT'S NOT GOOD.
IT'S NOT A GOOD IDEA.

28:58.301 --> 28:59.868
OH, PLEASE DON'T DO THAT.
COME ON. OH, PLEASE.

28:59.999 --> 29:01.957
I BEG YOU, PLEASE. I'M ON MY
KNEES. ALL RIGHT, STOP!

29:02.088 --> 29:04.046
-[PANTING]

29:04.177 --> 29:06.092
-LOOK, I HAVE A CONFESSION
TO MAKE.

29:06.222 --> 29:09.617
I'M NOT A COUNT.
I WASN'T AFTER YOU.
I WAS AFTER YOUR MONEY.

29:10.270 --> 29:12.359
I'M JUST A GIGOLO.

29:13.752 --> 29:15.014
-I DON'T CARE WHAT YOU ARE.

29:16.102 --> 29:17.756
I DON'T CARE
WHAT YOU'RE AFTER.

29:18.321 --> 29:20.976
YOU TURN ME ON.
KISS ME, YOU FOOL!

29:21.107 --> 29:22.412
-WHOA!

29:25.415 --> 29:29.550
-SO YOU'RE GOING TO
PLAY HARD TO GET. YES!

29:38.864 --> 29:39.995
-MR. ROGO.

29:40.517 --> 29:42.563
-YOU WERE CONFINED
TO YOUR ROOM, CARL.

29:46.175 --> 29:48.525
-I WAS JUST GETTING
SOME FRESH AIR, MR. ROGO.

29:48.656 --> 29:52.965
-I SAW YOU ON THE DANCE FLOOR,
CARL, SO DON'T INSULT ME
WITH YOUR FEEBLE EXCUSES.

29:53.574 --> 29:55.837
-LOOK, MR. ROGO,
I KNOW YOU'RE MAD AT ME,

29:55.968 --> 29:57.708
AND YOU HAVE EVERY RIGHT
TO BE SO.

29:58.927 --> 30:02.888
-I'M NOT MAD AT YOU, CARL.
I'M AFRAID OF YOU.
-YOU'RE AFRAID OF ME?

30:03.018 --> 30:06.500
-I'M AFRAID THAT YOUR LACK
OF PROFESSIONALISM WILL
COST ME MY LIFE.

30:08.807 --> 30:12.941
THAT'S WHY I CAME HERE,
TO LET YOU KNOW THAT THERE'S
BEEN A SLIGHT CHANGE IN PLANS.

30:13.072 --> 30:14.725
-OH, THAT'S GREAT.
WHAT ARE THEY?

30:15.378 --> 30:17.685
[SCREAMING]

30:20.949 --> 30:24.474
[CARL GAGGING]

30:41.274 --> 30:42.841
-I'M NOT SURE
THIS IS A GOOD IDEA.

30:42.971 --> 30:43.972
-WHY NOT?

30:45.974 --> 30:48.194
-WELL, FOR ONE THING,
YOU'RE UNDERAGE. THEY'RE
NOT GOING TO LET YOU GAMBLE.

30:49.021 --> 30:50.936
-LOOK, THEY DIDN'T CARD ME
IN MONTE CARLO.

30:51.066 --> 30:52.459
THEY'RE NOT GONNA CARD ME HERE.

30:52.589 --> 30:55.636
BESIDES,
I FEEL VERY LUCKY TONIGHT.

30:58.769 --> 30:59.858
-HI.
-HI.

31:01.424 --> 31:04.471
COULD YOU SHOW ME
SOME I.D., PLEASE?
-I.D.?

31:05.124 --> 31:08.954
YOU'RE KIDDING ME.
-SORRY, HOUSE RULES.
YOU MUST BE OVER 21 TO PLAY.

31:09.084 --> 31:10.607
-HATE TO SAY I TOLD YOU SO.

31:11.478 --> 31:13.959
OKAY, WE'LL PLAY ONE HAND,
THEN WE'RE OUT OF HERE.

31:25.622 --> 31:28.060
-BLACKJACK.
-ALL RIGHT!

31:30.366 --> 31:31.367
-SEVENTEEN.

31:39.636 --> 31:40.899
-MIGHT AS WELL LET IT RIDE.

31:46.730 --> 31:47.949
-STICK.

31:50.865 --> 31:53.737
-ODDS ARE SHE'S GOT 17.
GOTTA TAKE A HIT.

31:55.043 --> 31:56.001
-ALL RIGHT!

31:59.265 --> 32:03.312
YOU ARE PRETTY GOOD AT THIS.
-THAT WAS LUCK.

32:05.532 --> 32:07.055
YOURS MUST HAVE
RUBBED OFF ON ME.

32:22.462 --> 32:25.378
-BLACKJACK.
-OH, YOU ARE ON A ROLL.

32:27.467 --> 32:28.729
-SEVENTEEN.

33:31.705 --> 33:35.491
-[SCREAMING]

33:45.806 --> 33:48.069
-STEPHANIE? MAN OVERBOARD!

34:13.833 --> 34:14.878
-[COUGHING]

34:26.760 --> 34:31.069
MITCH! MITCH, SAVE ME!
MITCH, HELP ME!

34:32.244 --> 34:33.984
-TAKE THE RING.
TAKE THE RING!

34:38.467 --> 34:41.949
-HEY! HEY!
-COME BACK!

34:42.080 --> 34:44.081
-SOMEBODY, HELP! HEY!
-PLEASE!

34:44.995 --> 34:46.170
-HEY! HEY!

34:46.301 --> 34:48.695
-COME BACK! COME BACK!

34:49.870 --> 34:52.219
-WHAT'S YOUR LIMIT?
-$5,000 PER HAND.

34:56.877 --> 34:59.009
-YOU'RE BETTING $5,000
ON ONE HAND?

35:08.367 --> 35:09.324
-INSURANCE?

35:12.849 --> 35:16.549
-DOUBLE DOWN.
ONE CARD, $20,000 OR BUST.

35:26.820 --> 35:29.692
-HEY! COME BACK! COME BACK!

35:29.823 --> 35:33.087
COME BACK!
-IT'S ALL RIGHT.
THEY CAN'T HEAR US.

35:34.393 --> 35:35.655
THEY CAN'T HEAR US.

35:45.404 --> 35:49.538
COME HERE, COME HERE.
I GOT YOU. I GOT YOU.

35:49.669 --> 35:52.367
IT'S OKAY. IT'S OKAY.

36:12.953 --> 36:16.043
-[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]
